flowRoot.flowPara: At each node, pick best discrimator from sample of random input features, with respect to bootstrapped sample of depent variable
To predict for new y, pass input features through all trees. Average the values in leaf nodes for a single prediction
Each tree uses a subset of observations. The remainder (OOB: out-of-bag data), can be used to evaluate model performance as the model is built
A mehtod of measuring variable importance is to permute one feature and compare the RMSE on OOB with that of unpermuted
